WEBVTT

00:00:12.710 --> 00:00:15.310 line:80%
The conflict between Li and Wei
has become chaotic.

00:00:15.310 --> 00:00:18.570 line:80%
And you intend to establish
your own faction in the future.

00:00:19.120 --> 00:00:22.120 line:80%
Do you wish to make this chaos even worse?

00:00:34.910 --> 00:00:35.830 line:80%
As a man,

00:00:36.900 --> 00:00:38.830 line:80%
one must not be a fence-sitter.

00:00:39.970 --> 00:00:41.160 line:80%
As a minister,

00:00:42.400 --> 00:00:44.600 line:80%
one must not switch sides frivolously.

00:00:46.330 --> 00:00:47.800 line:80%
That is all I have to say.

00:00:49.390 --> 00:00:51.780 line:80%
Zheng! Zheng!

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:53.510 line:80%
Are you here?

00:00:54.680 --> 00:00:58.400 line:80%
Zheng, Mrs. Zhao
asked you to go back for lunch.

00:01:04.929 --> 00:01:07.790 line:80%
Young lady, why don't you
come in and sit for a while?

00:01:08.520 --> 00:01:11.680 line:80%
I'm not going into a villain's house.

00:01:11.710 --> 00:01:13.330 line:80%
Thank you, Mr. Scholar.

00:01:13.670 --> 00:01:15.330 line:80%
Why do you call me Mr. Scholar?

00:01:15.720 --> 00:01:19.630 line:80%
My sister said your carriage
was full of books.

00:01:22.010 --> 00:01:23.940 line:80%
I won't disturb your rest, My Lord.

00:01:25.310 --> 00:01:27.650 line:80%
Please pretend I was never here.

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:34.210 line:80%
Let's go.

00:02:19.640 --> 00:02:22.200 line:80%
Was that man really the Marquis of Wu'an?

00:02:29.270 --> 00:02:30.800 line:80%
He just broke a cup. So what?

00:02:31.710 --> 00:02:34.060 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an is nothing special.

00:02:39.480 --> 00:02:42.350 line:80%
His skills seem to have been improving.

00:04:11.120 --> 00:04:15.740 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:04:15.810 --> 00:04:18.420 line:80%
[Episode 11]

00:04:25.450 --> 00:04:26.440 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:04:36.920 --> 00:04:37.750 line:80%
Changyu!

00:04:39.160 --> 00:04:40.040 line:80%
Qianqian?

00:04:40.040 --> 00:04:42.690 line:80%
Which young lady has been doing dirty,
exhausting work all day

00:04:42.690 --> 00:04:44.090 line:80%
yet is still this pretty?

00:04:44.520 --> 00:04:46.070 line:80%
Hop on. I'll take you home.

00:04:46.800 --> 00:04:48.520 line:80%
No need. I'll go back myself.

00:04:48.520 --> 00:04:50.360 line:80%
Usually, I'd let you be,

00:04:50.360 --> 00:04:51.600 line:80%
but today I kept you here late

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:52.920 line:80%
because there were too many banquets.

00:04:52.920 --> 00:04:53.870 line:80%
It's already dark.

00:04:53.870 --> 00:04:56.400 line:80%
I'm worried about you
walking alone at night.

00:04:57.070 --> 00:04:57.840 line:80%
Get in.

00:04:59.400 --> 00:05:01.600 line:80%
It's okay. I can manage it alone.
You go.

00:05:01.840 --> 00:05:03.040 line:80%
Well then, thank you.

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:15.420 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:05:29.990 --> 00:05:30.720 line:80%
Come out.

00:05:34.110 --> 00:05:34.720 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:05:34.440 --> 00:05:37.720 line:80%
[Xie Wu, Blood-Robed Cavalry Guard]
[Xie Qi, Blood-Robed Cavalry Guard]

00:05:34.740 --> 00:05:35.600 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:05:35.870 --> 00:05:37.040 line:80%
we are late.

00:05:41.600 --> 00:05:42.470 line:80%
You may rise.

00:05:44.780 --> 00:05:45.910 line:80%
How many of you came?

00:05:46.880 --> 00:05:48.080 line:80%
Just Xie Qi and me.

00:05:48.340 --> 00:05:49.280 line:80%
We were afraid of being noticed,

00:05:49.280 --> 00:05:50.750 line:80%
so we didn't bring the other guards along.

00:05:50.750 --> 00:05:53.080 line:80%
Your Lordship, fortunately you are safe.

00:05:54.630 --> 00:05:56.490 line:80%
Unfortunately, Xie Yi and Xie San

00:05:57.320 --> 00:05:58.750 line:80%
died because of me.

00:06:01.750 --> 00:06:03.090 line:80%
We brothers once swore

00:06:03.160 --> 00:06:04.160 line:80%
to keep you safe

00:06:04.310 --> 00:06:05.910 line:80%
even at the cost of our lives.

00:06:07.960 --> 00:06:09.360 line:80%
No one from the Xie family

00:06:09.930 --> 00:06:11.440 line:80%
would die in vain.

00:06:11.960 --> 00:06:14.250 line:80%
All of us are hoping you return soon.

00:06:14.430 --> 00:06:17.230 line:80%
That Wei Xuan
is running rampant in the army.

00:06:18.100 --> 00:06:20.540 line:80%
He flaunts his power every day.

00:06:20.990 --> 00:06:22.530 line:80%
The brothers can hardly wait to tie him up

00:06:22.530 --> 00:06:23.840 line:80%
and throw him to the wolves.

00:06:23.840 --> 00:06:24.630 line:80%
Let him be.

00:06:26.960 --> 00:06:28.280 line:80%
Before long, a bloody battle

00:06:28.280 --> 00:06:31.610 line:80%
between us and Prince Changxin
in Chongzhou is inevitable.

00:06:31.750 --> 00:06:33.990 line:80%
Storing grain
is the top priority right now.

00:06:33.990 --> 00:06:35.630 line:80%
The Court refuses to release grain.

00:06:35.630 --> 00:06:37.480 line:80%
Wei Xuan has accepted Prime Minister Wei's
military order

00:06:37.480 --> 00:06:39.740 line:80%
and plans to requisition grain locally.

00:06:45.190 --> 00:06:46.270 line:80%
Sixteen years ago,

00:06:47.040 --> 00:06:48.970 line:80%
it was in Jinzhou where the Xie Army

00:06:49.450 --> 00:06:53.110 line:80%
suffered a crushing defeat due to
lack of provisions and support.

00:06:54.760 --> 00:06:57.290 line:80%
I absolutely cannot
repeat the same mistake.

00:06:59.430 --> 00:07:01.480 line:80%
Wei Xuan is ambitious
for great achievements.

00:07:01.480 --> 00:07:04.230 line:80%
It's only a matter of time
before he loses to Prince Changxin.

00:07:04.230 --> 00:07:05.690 line:80%
Let's just go with the flow

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:07.520 line:80%
and let Wei Xuan
and those idiots under his command

00:07:07.520 --> 00:07:08.430 line:80%
serve as bait

00:07:09.280 --> 00:07:11.520 line:80%
to lure Prince Changxin
to lead troops south.

00:07:11.520 --> 00:07:13.670 line:80%
By then, I will have my own strategy.

00:07:14.310 --> 00:07:17.570 line:80%
So, Your Lordship, you don't plan
to return to camp for now?

00:07:19.200 --> 00:07:20.320 line:80%
You go back first

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:22.480 line:80%
and spread the news of my death.

00:07:22.480 --> 00:07:24.340 line:80%
The more people know, the better.

00:07:24.520 --> 00:07:25.190 line:80%
Yes.

00:07:32.990 --> 00:07:33.630 line:80%
Go now.

00:07:33.880 --> 00:07:34.490 line:80%
Yes.

00:07:43.090 --> 00:07:45.040 line:80%
The braised pork is sold out today.

00:07:45.190 --> 00:07:46.959 line:80%
The pig head meat was very popular.

00:07:46.959 --> 00:07:47.600 line:80%
Really?

00:07:48.400 --> 00:07:51.390 line:80%
A few days ago, Mrs. Wang said
her daughter is getting married

00:07:51.390 --> 00:07:53.230 line:80%
and ordered half a side of pork from me.

00:07:53.230 --> 00:07:55.090 line:80%
Won't that mean more work for you?

00:07:55.430 --> 00:07:57.280 line:80%
I welcome this kind of work.

00:08:02.100 --> 00:08:04.000 line:80%
Who is it? Who are you?

00:08:07.750 --> 00:08:09.210 line:80%
I'll go out and take a look.

00:08:23.750 --> 00:08:25.800 line:80%
Qianqian, don't come out now.

00:08:26.310 --> 00:08:27.670 line:80%
I'll deal with them.

00:08:27.750 --> 00:08:28.430 line:80%
Beat her.

00:08:40.640 --> 00:08:41.839 line:80%
Who sent you?

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:43.160 line:80%
Was it him?

00:08:43.180 --> 00:08:45.580 line:80%
Why won't he let me go
after all these years?

00:08:50.280 --> 00:08:53.120 line:80%
Help! Help!

00:09:05.760 --> 00:09:06.890 line:80%
Changyu, watch out!

00:09:13.550 --> 00:09:15.350 line:80%
Don't run!

00:09:15.640 --> 00:09:17.430 line:80%
This voice sounds familiar.

00:09:20.690 --> 00:09:21.780 line:80%
Butcher Guo.

00:09:22.160 --> 00:09:23.120 line:80%
Butcher Guo?

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:24.880 line:80%
Mrs. Fan...

00:09:25.400 --> 00:09:26.240 line:80%
Heroine Fan.

00:09:26.710 --> 00:09:27.840 line:80%
Mommy!

00:09:28.400 --> 00:09:29.590 line:80%
I just lost my mind for a moment.

00:09:29.590 --> 00:09:31.470 line:80%
You've gone against me time and again.

00:09:31.470 --> 00:09:33.280 line:80%
That doesn't look like losing your mind
for a moment.

00:09:33.280 --> 00:09:34.830 line:80%
Someone paid us

00:09:34.830 --> 00:09:36.040 line:80%
to kill you.

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:38.550 line:80%
Who?

00:09:38.880 --> 00:09:39.550 line:80%
Who?

00:09:39.590 --> 00:09:40.280 line:80%
Who?

00:09:42.400 --> 00:09:43.120 line:80%
Who!

00:09:43.760 --> 00:09:44.520 line:80%
Changyu!

00:09:48.470 --> 00:09:49.430 line:80%
Since we're selling one,

00:09:49.430 --> 00:09:50.830 line:80%
we might as well sell two!

00:09:58.550 --> 00:09:59.910 line:80%
Go to hell!

00:10:00.070 --> 00:10:02.710 line:80%
Bastard! Come at me if you have the guts!

00:10:04.310 --> 00:10:06.040 line:80%
I'll come at you then!

00:10:06.120 --> 00:10:06.920 line:80%
Changyu!

00:10:08.310 --> 00:10:08.830 line:80%
I...

00:10:18.130 --> 00:10:20.080 line:80%
Changyu! Changyu?

00:10:23.620 --> 00:10:24.750 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:10:35.890 --> 00:10:38.530 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:10:39.850 --> 00:10:42.200 line:80%
Yan Zheng, did you see Changyu?

00:10:43.150 --> 00:10:44.280 line:80%
What's happening here?

00:10:44.280 --> 00:10:46.520 line:80%
-She was drugged. Go get some water.
-Okay.

00:10:46.520 --> 00:10:48.030 line:80%
Honey, come help.

00:10:48.550 --> 00:10:49.880 line:80%
Hello, sir. Hello, sir.

00:11:03.250 --> 00:11:04.700 line:80%
What's happening here?

00:11:06.900 --> 00:11:07.860 line:80%
What?

00:11:07.950 --> 00:11:09.780 line:80%
My butt... hurts.

00:11:09.830 --> 00:11:10.710 line:80%
Hurts?

00:11:10.760 --> 00:11:11.670 line:80%
Where does it hurt?

00:11:11.670 --> 00:11:12.850 line:80%
My butt!

00:11:12.880 --> 00:11:13.640 line:80%
Your butt what?

00:11:13.640 --> 00:11:15.120 line:80%
My butt hurts!

00:11:15.240 --> 00:11:16.970 line:80%
Why hasn't the pain killed you?

00:11:29.280 --> 00:11:30.650 line:80%
Despicable man!

00:11:33.430 --> 00:11:34.360 line:80%
Please spare me.

00:11:34.400 --> 00:11:35.640 line:80%
Please spare me!

00:11:35.640 --> 00:11:37.800 line:80%
I'm not a bandit from Qingfeng Stronghold.

00:11:37.800 --> 00:11:40.830 line:80%
I was bullied by those two broads—

00:11:41.510 --> 00:11:42.080 line:80%
no—

00:11:42.590 --> 00:11:43.880 line:80%
those two ladies from Yixiang Restaurant.

00:11:43.880 --> 00:11:46.190 line:80%
I just wanted to scare them.

00:11:49.280 --> 00:11:50.240 line:80%
Guo!

00:11:50.520 --> 00:11:52.310 line:80%
You took your grudge against Fan Erniu

00:11:52.310 --> 00:11:54.350 line:80%
out on this poor orphan girl?

00:11:54.370 --> 00:11:55.640 line:80%
Are you even human?

00:11:55.640 --> 00:11:56.400 line:80%
My butt...

00:11:56.420 --> 00:11:58.000 line:80%
Say no more.

00:11:58.000 --> 00:12:00.120 line:80%
Do you think the fire isn't big enough?

00:12:00.120 --> 00:12:02.400 line:80%
Do you want to blow the roof off?

00:12:03.880 --> 00:12:05.120 line:80%
It hurts!

00:12:11.830 --> 00:12:12.890 line:80%
Just to scare them?

00:12:13.880 --> 00:12:15.550 line:80%
Didn't you drug her?

00:12:16.550 --> 00:12:18.040 line:80%
What exactly did you want?

00:12:19.590 --> 00:12:22.000 line:80%
I wanted to knock them out first...

00:12:26.240 --> 00:12:27.040 line:80%
And then?

00:12:32.310 --> 00:12:33.040 line:80%
Speak!

00:12:34.240 --> 00:12:36.280 line:80%
Then destroy her meridians...

00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:40.760 line:80%
Is that all?

00:12:46.970 --> 00:12:48.920 line:80%
And sell her to the mountains...

00:13:01.430 --> 00:13:02.310 line:80%
Stop!

00:13:03.430 --> 00:13:04.430 line:80%
Yan, doing this

00:13:04.870 --> 00:13:06.400 line:80%
will only dirty your hands.

00:13:06.790 --> 00:13:07.880 line:80%
How he should be punished

00:13:07.880 --> 00:13:08.890 line:80%
is for the authorities to decide.

00:13:08.890 --> 00:13:11.900 line:80%
The authorities?
If I hadn't been here today,

00:13:12.280 --> 00:13:14.550 line:80%
something bad would have happened
to Changyu.

00:13:14.550 --> 00:13:17.400 line:80%
If you accept your fate, who can save you?

00:13:19.240 --> 00:13:20.470 line:80%
I will take

00:13:21.240 --> 00:13:22.480 line:80%
my own revenge!

00:13:24.280 --> 00:13:24.880 line:80%
Stop!

00:13:24.880 --> 00:13:25.400 line:80%
No!

00:13:25.520 --> 00:13:26.280 line:80%
Yan Zheng!

00:13:32.040 --> 00:13:32.920 line:80%
Don't kill him.

00:13:33.590 --> 00:13:34.590 line:80%
It's not worth it.

00:13:50.880 --> 00:13:51.760 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:13:53.070 --> 00:13:53.760 line:80%
Lie down.

00:13:57.950 --> 00:13:59.280 line:80%
Rest assured and sleep.

00:13:59.560 --> 00:14:00.530 line:80%
I won't kill him.

00:14:11.470 --> 00:14:13.850 line:80%
Alright, don't cry.

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:16.570 line:80%
I have plenty of strength.

00:14:16.600 --> 00:14:17.310 line:80%
Look.

00:14:18.310 --> 00:14:19.400 line:80%
My hands are fine,

00:14:19.400 --> 00:14:20.730 line:80%
and my feet are fine too.

00:14:20.950 --> 00:14:21.680 line:80%
Stop crying.

00:14:27.670 --> 00:14:28.880 line:80%
Changyu...

00:14:33.240 --> 00:14:35.370 line:80%
Help me get a basin of warm water, okay?

00:14:36.760 --> 00:14:37.640 line:80%
Okay.

00:14:53.000 --> 00:14:55.190 line:80%
How is it? Does your head still hurt?

00:14:56.550 --> 00:14:59.350 line:80%
Do you feel uncomfortable anywhere else?

00:15:01.280 --> 00:15:03.010 line:80%
If you had killed someone for me

00:15:03.770 --> 00:15:04.840 line:80%
and gone to prison,

00:15:06.940 --> 00:15:08.400 line:80%
my head would really hurt.

00:15:25.000 --> 00:15:25.880 line:80%
Promise me.

00:15:27.240 --> 00:15:28.570 line:80%
Don't get into trouble.

00:15:34.880 --> 00:15:35.710 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:15:37.760 --> 00:15:39.090 line:80%
I'll be fine.

00:15:53.050 --> 00:15:56.100 line:80%
Manager, the doors and windows are locked.

00:15:56.830 --> 00:15:58.840 line:80%
The water vats for fire are full.

00:15:59.880 --> 00:16:01.090 line:80%
And I've assigned the boys

00:16:01.090 --> 00:16:03.290 line:80%
to take shifts to guard every two hours.

00:16:03.470 --> 00:16:05.070 line:80%
Do you have any other orders?

00:16:06.930 --> 00:16:10.880 line:80%
Manager, is there going to be a war?

00:16:13.440 --> 00:16:16.570 line:80%
Add 2 more locks tomorrow.

00:16:17.070 --> 00:16:19.390 line:80%
There are already 3 locks on 2 doors.

00:16:19.470 --> 00:16:21.240 line:80%
You still want to add more?

00:16:21.670 --> 00:16:22.280 line:80%
Yes.

00:16:22.950 --> 00:16:24.010 line:80%
Add one more layer,

00:16:24.590 --> 00:16:27.720 line:80%
and reinforce the door frames with iron.

00:16:28.830 --> 00:16:29.550 line:80%
Okay.

00:17:47.620 --> 00:17:48.290 line:80%
Mom.

00:17:48.770 --> 00:17:50.370 line:80%
Were you good today, Bao'er?

00:17:50.610 --> 00:17:51.640 line:80%
Very good.

00:17:51.900 --> 00:17:53.260 line:80%
I didn't go out at all.

00:17:53.680 --> 00:17:57.010 line:80%
I finished
all the homework you left for me.

00:17:58.330 --> 00:17:59.530 line:80%
Such a good boy?

00:18:00.350 --> 00:18:03.000 line:80%
Let's be this good tomorrow too, okay?

00:18:14.420 --> 00:18:16.520 line:80%
[Luyuan]

00:18:43.960 --> 00:18:44.760 line:80%
Great move!

00:18:44.760 --> 00:18:45.310 line:80%
Great...

00:18:48.480 --> 00:18:50.590 line:80%
An Xu, so you know how to play Go?

00:18:51.390 --> 00:18:52.480 line:80%
Just a little.

00:18:53.910 --> 00:18:56.110 line:80%
How about playing a round with me?

00:18:56.110 --> 00:18:56.760 line:80%
Sure.

00:18:59.040 --> 00:18:59.650 line:80%
Alright.

00:19:10.830 --> 00:19:12.030 line:80%
That was satisfying!

00:19:12.360 --> 00:19:14.360 line:80%
Let's play another round tomorrow.

00:19:14.800 --> 00:19:15.440 line:80%
Okay.

00:19:17.480 --> 00:19:18.210 line:80%
Headmaster.

00:19:23.000 --> 00:19:25.870 line:80%
When I was young,
I read a fragment of a Go manual

00:19:26.350 --> 00:19:27.880 line:80%
called "The Mystery of Qi."

00:19:28.110 --> 00:19:30.760 line:80%
I heard that your Library
has over 10,000 books.

00:19:30.760 --> 00:19:32.000 line:80%
I wanted to find it,

00:19:32.520 --> 00:19:34.180 line:80%
but I haven't been able to yet.

00:19:34.910 --> 00:19:36.000 line:80%
This book

00:19:36.110 --> 00:19:37.760 line:80%
is indeed not in the Library.

00:19:39.240 --> 00:19:39.960 line:80%
However,

00:19:40.440 --> 00:19:42.110 line:80%
in the Gongsun family's collection,

00:19:42.110 --> 00:19:44.170 line:80%
there is actually a complete volume.

00:19:44.480 --> 00:19:46.910 line:80%
Unfortunately,
it is my grandfather's treasure

00:19:46.910 --> 00:19:48.170 line:80%
and cannot be lent out.

00:19:53.080 --> 00:19:54.590 line:80%
A gentleman
does not take what others love.

00:19:54.590 --> 00:19:56.040 line:80%
It is natural for Old Mr. Gongsun

00:19:56.040 --> 00:19:57.300 line:80%
to cherish treasures.

00:20:01.590 --> 00:20:02.520 line:80%
However...

00:20:04.400 --> 00:20:06.680 line:80%
Although it cannot be lent out,

00:20:07.590 --> 00:20:09.410 line:80%
I can copy the fragment of the Go manual

00:20:09.410 --> 00:20:10.850 line:80%
and give it to you.

00:20:12.440 --> 00:20:13.370 line:80%
Thank you, Headmaster.

00:20:13.370 --> 00:20:22.200 line:80%
[Penetration and Subtlety]

00:20:29.440 --> 00:20:30.430 line:80%
A ruler

00:20:30.590 --> 00:20:34.250 line:80%
should bear the responsibility
of protecting the common people.

00:20:53.830 --> 00:20:56.150 line:80%
Consort Dowager An,

00:20:56.520 --> 00:20:58.380 line:80%
our new student An Xu

00:20:58.760 --> 00:21:01.220 line:80%
is actually the Princess Royal
in disguise.

00:21:01.350 --> 00:21:02.780 line:80%
I have noticed this

00:21:02.830 --> 00:21:04.200 line:80%
and dare not keep it hidden.

00:21:04.200 --> 00:21:06.860 line:80%
I report it
for Your Highness's consideration.

00:21:08.080 --> 00:21:10.080 line:80%
[Yixiang Restaurant]

00:21:15.150 --> 00:21:15.960 line:80%
Qianqian?

00:21:17.350 --> 00:21:18.070 line:80%
Qianqian?

00:21:28.460 --> 00:21:29.310 line:80%
Where is she?

00:21:46.790 --> 00:21:47.510 line:80%
Changyu.

00:21:48.910 --> 00:21:50.350 line:80%
You scared me.

00:21:50.370 --> 00:21:51.570 line:80%
You asked me to come,

00:21:51.600 --> 00:21:52.590 line:80%
but you weren't here.

00:21:52.590 --> 00:21:53.920 line:80%
I was about to leave.

00:21:54.510 --> 00:21:55.470 line:80%
Go sit down.

00:22:04.720 --> 00:22:06.050 line:80%
Are you feeling better?

00:22:06.070 --> 00:22:07.350 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:22:07.590 --> 00:22:09.550 line:80%
You sent me medicine and food.

00:22:09.550 --> 00:22:10.950 line:80%
I've even gained weight.

00:22:12.390 --> 00:22:13.190 line:80%
How about you?

00:22:13.960 --> 00:22:16.310 line:80%
Were you scared that night?

00:22:17.170 --> 00:22:18.170 line:80%
If you're afraid,

00:22:18.200 --> 00:22:19.280 line:80%
you can tell me.

00:22:19.480 --> 00:22:20.660 line:80%
Don't bottle it up.

00:22:20.830 --> 00:22:22.000 line:80%
It was nothing.

00:22:22.000 --> 00:22:23.150 line:80%
I've seen it all.

00:22:23.630 --> 00:22:25.000 line:80%
Just because a bad guy scared me
with a stick,

00:22:25.000 --> 00:22:27.330 line:80%
does that mean
I should be scared to death?

00:22:27.720 --> 00:22:29.540 line:80%
But your husband...

00:22:29.680 --> 00:22:31.340 line:80%
He was quite scary that night.

00:22:31.480 --> 00:22:33.010 line:80%
He's not usually like that.

00:22:33.750 --> 00:22:35.910 line:80%
He just can't stand anyone hurting me.

00:22:36.280 --> 00:22:37.800 line:80%
I know.

00:22:37.800 --> 00:22:39.060 line:80%
You two love each other,

00:22:39.060 --> 00:22:40.790 line:80%
and it makes everyone jealous.

00:22:40.830 --> 00:22:41.440 line:80%
By the way,

00:22:42.240 --> 00:22:43.040 line:80%
look at this.

00:22:43.350 --> 00:22:44.520 line:80%
Times are chaotic now.

00:22:44.520 --> 00:22:46.520 line:80%
We must learn to protect ourselves.

00:22:51.680 --> 00:22:53.720 line:80%
What is this?

00:22:53.870 --> 00:22:55.070 line:80%
Cornel water.

00:22:55.590 --> 00:22:57.390 line:80%
I got a bigger bottle this time.

00:22:57.440 --> 00:22:58.960 line:80%
Last time it ran out at a critical moment.

00:22:58.960 --> 00:23:00.220 line:80%
This should be enough.

00:23:00.280 --> 00:23:01.810 line:80%
If sprayed in the eyes, it causes
swelling, pain,

00:23:01.810 --> 00:23:03.810 line:80%
and temporary blindness for 3 days.

00:23:04.180 --> 00:23:06.640 line:80%
I didn't know cornel
could be used like that.

00:23:07.350 --> 00:23:09.800 line:80%
Is this what you used on Butcher Guo?

00:23:11.070 --> 00:23:12.590 line:80%
If that's the case,

00:23:12.960 --> 00:23:16.200 line:80%
garlic, ginger,
and peppercorns could work too.

00:23:19.520 --> 00:23:20.960 line:80%
That Guo got off easy.

00:23:36.110 --> 00:23:36.840 line:80%
Headmaster?

00:23:42.280 --> 00:23:44.310 line:80%
I remember someone playing Go with me

00:23:44.310 --> 00:23:47.100 line:80%
from a distance in the Fengyu Pavilion.

00:23:47.720 --> 00:23:51.520 line:80%
Our moves went back and forth,
breaking stalemates again and again.

00:23:52.110 --> 00:23:54.150 line:80%
Who is playing Go here?

00:23:54.720 --> 00:23:57.310 line:80%
Looks like the game isn't over.

00:24:04.680 --> 00:24:05.760 line:80%
I'll place it here.

00:24:07.590 --> 00:24:08.310 line:80%
Is that so?

00:24:09.830 --> 00:24:12.360 line:80%
That was really a meeting
of kindred spirits.

00:24:14.800 --> 00:24:16.600 line:80%
Another white piece was placed!

00:24:17.150 --> 00:24:18.000 line:80%
Look.

00:24:20.340 --> 00:24:21.430 line:80%
Your Highness,

00:24:21.450 --> 00:24:23.650 line:80%
I think someone is inviting you to play.

00:24:24.370 --> 00:24:27.030 line:80%
I'm the one who intruded
on someone else's game.

00:24:29.910 --> 00:24:31.480 line:80%
I also have a friend

00:24:31.480 --> 00:24:32.740 line:80%
who is excellent at Go.

00:24:33.550 --> 00:24:34.350 line:80%
But...

00:24:35.240 --> 00:24:36.590 line:80%
we've never met.

00:24:37.720 --> 00:24:38.850 line:80%
What a coincidence.

00:24:39.120 --> 00:24:40.980 line:80%
Go reveals a gentleman's virtue.

00:24:41.310 --> 00:24:43.380 line:80%
Although I haven't seen my opponent,

00:24:44.000 --> 00:24:46.950 line:80%
I can glimpse his thoughts
through the game.

00:24:47.110 --> 00:24:49.840 line:80%
Playing remotely
is like having a conversation.

00:24:50.600 --> 00:24:51.570 line:80%
It's all about

00:24:52.000 --> 00:24:53.550 line:80%
that moment of connection.

00:25:16.310 --> 00:25:18.070 line:80%
How do I compare

00:25:18.830 --> 00:25:19.690 line:80%
to your friend?

00:25:22.960 --> 00:25:26.240 line:80%
Although we haven't met,

00:25:27.130 --> 00:25:29.260 line:80%
your Go skills are better than theirs.

00:25:31.680 --> 00:25:34.070 line:80%
Once I get your "The Mystery of Qi",

00:25:34.310 --> 00:25:36.370 line:80%
my skills will improve even further.

00:25:39.960 --> 00:25:40.870 line:80%
Perhaps...

00:25:42.040 --> 00:25:43.800 line:80%
I'll be able to meet him soon.

00:25:47.040 --> 00:25:48.110 line:80%
In that case,

00:25:48.480 --> 00:25:49.760 line:80%
when you meet,

00:25:50.150 --> 00:25:52.280 line:80%
you must play a game together.

00:25:54.200 --> 00:25:55.000 line:80%
Young Master!

00:25:55.240 --> 00:25:57.640 line:80%
Y-Young Master! Someone from home is here.

00:25:58.930 --> 00:25:59.690 line:80%
Home?

00:26:08.070 --> 00:26:09.590 line:80%
Your Highness.

00:26:12.070 --> 00:26:16.200 line:80%
I have been ordered
to ask you to return to the palace.

00:26:44.190 --> 00:26:47.730 line:80%
[Seeking Truth in the Classics]

00:26:45.150 --> 00:26:47.610 line:80%
I don't know how
the Consort Dowager learned

00:26:47.800 --> 00:26:50.000 line:80%
that you swapped identities with Mr. An

00:26:50.240 --> 00:26:52.040 line:80%
and came to study at Luyuan Academy.

00:26:52.040 --> 00:26:53.170 line:80%
What did Mother say?

00:26:54.760 --> 00:26:57.690 line:80%
Her Highness has confined Mr. An.

00:26:58.150 --> 00:27:00.630 line:80%
She's furious about this.

00:27:00.800 --> 00:27:03.630 line:80%
She originally allowed you
to return to the Capital next month,

00:27:03.630 --> 00:27:06.360 line:80%
but now you'll have to return
to the palace today.

00:27:08.740 --> 00:27:10.470 line:80%
Your Highness.

00:27:10.790 --> 00:27:13.890 line:80%
I've had people seal the backyard.

00:27:14.200 --> 00:27:16.960 line:80%
No one will notice your departure.

00:27:17.480 --> 00:27:22.330 line:80%
The academy will claim An Xu withdrew
for personal reasons.

00:27:22.550 --> 00:27:24.720 line:80%
This will save everyone's face.

00:27:25.590 --> 00:27:27.280 line:80%
You are thorough, Nanny.

00:27:28.590 --> 00:27:30.450 line:80%
I apologize for my incompetence.

00:27:30.520 --> 00:27:33.040 line:80%
Your Highness, please.

00:27:39.520 --> 00:27:40.310 line:80%
Master,

00:27:41.460 --> 00:27:42.790 line:80%
for the past half month,

00:27:43.330 --> 00:27:45.530 line:80%
have you been the one playing Go with me?

00:27:45.890 --> 00:27:47.870 line:80%
I did not expect that

00:27:48.010 --> 00:27:49.840 line:80%
the one playing chess here every day

00:27:49.840 --> 00:27:51.930 line:80%
would be a lady.

00:27:56.390 --> 00:27:57.200 line:80%
Right.

00:27:58.240 --> 00:28:00.440 line:80%
Those who
can be in Guangling Temple every day

00:28:00.440 --> 00:28:02.500 line:80%
could only be the monks of the temple.

00:28:03.870 --> 00:28:05.200 line:80%
I overthought it.

00:28:11.710 --> 00:28:14.710 line:80%
To play Go remotely in this pavilion

00:28:14.760 --> 00:28:17.760 line:80%
implies a destined bond.

00:28:17.760 --> 00:28:21.200 line:80%
Gongsun, why sever this connection?

00:28:22.350 --> 00:28:24.240 line:80%
I am but a carefree idler,

00:28:24.240 --> 00:28:25.570 line:80%
with nothing to my name.

00:28:26.110 --> 00:28:28.170 line:80%
How could I dare to hold up such a lady?

00:28:29.910 --> 00:28:32.810 line:80%
It was fine
when I didn't know she was a girl.

00:28:33.200 --> 00:28:34.590 line:80%
But now that I know,

00:28:35.110 --> 00:28:37.570 line:80%
it would be improper
to disturb her further.

00:28:39.630 --> 00:28:40.990 line:80%
I remember

00:28:41.680 --> 00:28:45.340 line:80%
someone playing Go with me
from a distance in the Fengyu Pavilion.

00:28:45.580 --> 00:28:46.910 line:80%
Our moves went back and forth,

00:28:46.910 --> 00:28:49.040 line:80%
breaking stalemates again and again.

00:28:53.440 --> 00:28:54.960 line:80%
I also have a friend

00:28:54.960 --> 00:28:56.220 line:80%
who is excellent at Go.

00:28:57.390 --> 00:28:58.520 line:80%
But...

00:28:58.520 --> 00:28:59.800 line:80%
we have never met.

00:29:00.280 --> 00:29:01.410 line:80%
What a coincidence.

00:29:02.720 --> 00:29:03.720 line:80%
Perhaps...

00:29:04.630 --> 00:29:06.390 line:80%
I'll be able to meet him soon.

00:29:16.660 --> 00:29:17.320 line:80%
Please.

00:29:45.420 --> 00:29:48.010 line:80%
Do you know why I came back?

00:29:58.520 --> 00:29:59.780 line:80%
The road ahead is long.

00:30:00.010 --> 00:30:03.410 line:80%
I only wish for Your Highness
to return to the capital safely.

00:30:07.480 --> 00:30:09.140 line:80%
You knew my identity long ago?

00:30:10.880 --> 00:30:14.010 line:80%
I only found out your identity
the day before yesterday.

00:30:15.560 --> 00:30:17.690 line:80%
When you first arrived at the academy,

00:30:18.040 --> 00:30:20.330 line:80%
I noticed that you were a woman.

00:30:21.440 --> 00:30:22.440 line:80%
Who is An Xu?

00:30:23.440 --> 00:30:24.280 line:80%
An Xu.

00:30:24.520 --> 00:30:25.520 line:80%
He's calling you.

00:30:26.480 --> 00:30:27.480 line:80%
Mr. An.

00:30:28.480 --> 00:30:30.850 line:80%
You look so outstanding,

00:30:30.020 --> 00:30:31.660 line:80%
♪ I just don't want to ♪

00:30:31.070 --> 00:30:32.550 line:80%
magnificent,

00:30:32.280 --> 00:30:33.130 line:80%
♪ Keep weighing every word ♪

00:30:33.150 --> 00:30:35.320 line:80%
♪ And hiding in time in silence ♪

00:30:33.550 --> 00:30:35.070 line:80%
and distinguished.

00:30:36.240 --> 00:30:37.640 line:80%
I just didn't expect

00:30:36.310 --> 00:30:38.070 line:80%
♪ It's not that I don't believe in karma ♪

00:30:38.550 --> 00:30:40.100 line:80%
that you were actually
the current Princess Royal.

00:30:38.730 --> 00:30:40.890 line:80%
♪ That I'm being stubborn ♪

00:30:42.610 --> 00:30:44.360 line:80%
♪ Some endings have long been ♪

00:30:44.630 --> 00:30:46.890 line:80%
I came to this academy for someone.

00:30:44.950 --> 00:30:46.220 line:80%
♪ Weathered through a thousand years ♪

00:30:46.250 --> 00:30:48.240 line:80%
♪ Traced by those who come after ♪

00:30:48.850 --> 00:30:50.790 line:80%
♪ Compared to fading away in sorrow ♪

00:30:51.290 --> 00:30:53.520 line:80%
♪ I'd rather fight ♪

00:30:54.300 --> 00:30:57.000 line:80%
♪ Life's bitterness ♪

00:30:57.490 --> 00:30:59.890 line:80%
♪ Comes from love ♪

00:31:00.700 --> 00:31:03.260 line:80%
♪ Love, yet so hard to hold ♪

00:31:03.730 --> 00:31:06.510 line:80%
♪ Like holing a torch in the wilderness ♪

00:31:04.960 --> 00:31:07.960 line:80%
That the Princess Royal favors our academy

00:31:07.170 --> 00:31:09.330 line:80%
♪ Time sings a mournful song ♪

00:31:07.980 --> 00:31:10.050 line:80%
is an honor for us all.

00:31:10.040 --> 00:31:12.380 line:80%
♪ Gathered little yet parted often ♪

00:31:13.200 --> 00:31:16.230 line:80%
♪ Just as tears fall into the long river ♪

00:31:16.620 --> 00:31:20.430 line:80%
This is the Go manual
I copied for you as I promised,

00:31:16.670 --> 00:31:21.610 line:80%
♪ I must dive into the starry stream ♪

00:31:21.680 --> 00:31:22.830 line:80%
"The Mystery of Qi."

00:31:23.760 --> 00:31:24.430 line:80%
♪ Don't mind me ♪

00:31:24.450 --> 00:31:25.440 line:80%
♪ Everything has happened ♪

00:31:24.790 --> 00:31:27.100 line:80%
I'm giving it to you now

00:31:25.800 --> 00:31:29.080 line:80%
♪ A thousand years from now
no one's blood will remain warm ♪

00:31:27.900 --> 00:31:29.180 line:80%
as a parting gift.

00:31:29.920 --> 00:31:31.820 line:80%
♪ Let them laugh and mock ♪

00:31:32.390 --> 00:31:35.480 line:80%
♪ I just want you to remember me ♪

00:31:36.280 --> 00:31:36.850 line:80%
♪ Don't care about ♪

00:31:36.870 --> 00:31:38.000 line:80%
♪ Leaving a name in history ♪

00:31:38.680 --> 00:31:41.790 line:80%
♪ I only want to leave a mark
in your life ♪

00:31:42.590 --> 00:31:43.980 line:80%
♪ I will let go ♪

00:31:45.020 --> 00:31:48.260 line:80%
♪ After taking this one last gamble ♪

00:31:48.890 --> 00:31:49.530 line:80%
♪ Don't mind ♪

00:31:49.550 --> 00:31:50.740 line:80%
♪ The carved stones or constellations ♪

00:31:51.300 --> 00:31:54.190 line:80%
♪ I'll cast all karma behind me ♪

00:31:55.170 --> 00:31:57.080 line:80%
♪ Playing war with the lords ♪

00:31:57.570 --> 00:32:01.200 line:80%
♪ Leaving no trace of fate ♪

00:32:18.940 --> 00:32:20.700 line:80%
Headmaster. Headmaster.

00:32:24.550 --> 00:32:26.830 line:80%
It is so late. Why are you still up?

00:32:28.240 --> 00:32:30.590 line:80%
An asked me to pass this letter to you.

00:32:51.190 --> 00:32:52.360 line:80%
So it was her.

00:32:59.750 --> 00:33:00.890 line:80%
In this game of Go,

00:33:03.510 --> 00:33:05.830 line:80%
I was utterly crushed.

00:33:18.460 --> 00:33:21.640 line:80%
[Composed]

00:33:23.960 --> 00:33:25.280 line:80%
Your Highness.

00:33:26.100 --> 00:33:29.100 line:80%
Since Princess Royal
returned from the river region,

00:33:29.150 --> 00:33:31.530 line:80%
she has stayed behind closed doors

00:33:31.950 --> 00:33:34.590 line:80%
and barely touched her meals.

00:33:35.310 --> 00:33:37.730 line:80%
It seems Gongsun Yin has no affection

00:33:37.830 --> 00:33:40.370 line:80%
for the Princess Royal.

00:33:41.150 --> 00:33:42.870 line:80%
If she knows,

00:33:42.870 --> 00:33:45.000 line:80%
she would be heartbroken.

00:33:45.440 --> 00:33:47.870 line:80%
The Gongsun family
even sent a personal letter,

00:33:47.870 --> 00:33:49.200 line:80%
sincere in their words.

00:33:50.440 --> 00:33:52.670 line:80%
I was a little surprised.

00:33:52.760 --> 00:33:56.100 line:80%
But with Her Highness's temperament,

00:33:56.240 --> 00:33:58.750 line:80%
she probably won't give up easily.

00:34:04.750 --> 00:34:06.510 line:80%
Shu is still young

00:34:05.230 --> 00:34:09.030 line:80%
[Consort Dowager An, Mother of Qi Shu]

00:34:06.530 --> 00:34:08.860 line:80%
and doesn't understand
all the complexities.

00:34:08.860 --> 00:34:10.760 line:80%
The Gongsun family may have prestige,

00:34:10.760 --> 00:34:12.720 line:80%
but after all,
they are not a suitable match.

00:34:12.720 --> 00:34:14.740 line:80%
You are right, Your Highness.

00:34:15.350 --> 00:34:18.760 line:80%
How should we persuade Her Highness?

00:34:19.720 --> 00:34:22.580 line:80%
Grand Tutor Li
has a reputation for virtue in court.

00:34:23.019 --> 00:34:25.110 line:80%
His eldest grandson, Li Huai'an,

00:34:25.140 --> 00:34:27.740 line:80%
is said to have achieved much
in the Northwest.

00:34:28.370 --> 00:34:30.490 line:80%
He's also a man of great appearance

00:34:31.350 --> 00:34:33.600 line:80%
and could be considered a suitable match.

00:34:33.600 --> 00:34:35.830 line:80%
Perhaps we should find a chance

00:34:36.130 --> 00:34:38.030 line:80%
and arrange a meeting between him and Shu.

00:34:38.030 --> 00:34:40.360 line:80%
I'll make the arrangements immediately.

00:34:45.680 --> 00:34:46.430 line:80%
Shu,

00:34:47.510 --> 00:34:49.240 line:80%
don't blame me for being harsh.

00:34:49.560 --> 00:34:50.950 line:80%
No matter how unwilling you are now,

00:34:50.950 --> 00:34:52.810 line:80%
you'll understand in the future.

00:34:57.330 --> 00:35:01.800 line:80%
[Three days later]

00:35:10.800 --> 00:35:12.430 line:80%
A blind date with the Princess Royal?

00:35:12.430 --> 00:35:13.760 line:80%
It seems my grandfather

00:35:14.030 --> 00:35:16.830 line:80%
is still obsessed with his rivalry
against Wei Yan

00:35:17.160 --> 00:35:19.120 line:80%
and wants to help me secure a footing

00:35:19.120 --> 00:35:20.580 line:80%
among the royal nobility.

00:35:22.200 --> 00:35:23.280 line:80%
In the end,

00:35:24.760 --> 00:35:27.120 line:80%
it's just party disputes.

00:35:28.390 --> 00:35:29.600 line:80%
It brings no benefit

00:35:30.080 --> 00:35:31.680 line:80%
to the stability of the state

00:35:31.760 --> 00:35:33.360 line:80%
or the welfare of the people.

00:35:36.030 --> 00:35:36.800 line:80%
My Lord.

00:35:37.910 --> 00:35:39.760 line:80%
The Grand Tutor is your grandfather.

00:35:39.760 --> 00:35:41.490 line:80%
You should try to persuade him.

00:35:43.240 --> 00:35:44.570 line:80%
I may be short-sighted,

00:35:45.430 --> 00:35:47.060 line:80%
but all these years at the border,

00:35:47.060 --> 00:35:51.530 line:80%
[To my grandson, Huai'an]

00:35:47.750 --> 00:35:50.480 line:80%
whether it was General He
or the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:35:50.720 --> 00:35:52.310 line:80%
although they belong to the Wei faction,

00:35:52.310 --> 00:35:53.640 line:80%
they were fearless in battle

00:35:53.640 --> 00:35:55.560 line:80%
and good men who defended the border.

00:35:55.560 --> 00:35:57.160 line:80%
Grandfather has given orders.

00:35:57.160 --> 00:35:58.820 line:80%
I have no choice but to go back.

00:36:00.390 --> 00:36:01.280 line:80%
Fortunately,

00:36:02.570 --> 00:36:04.570 line:80%
the Marquis of Wu'an is still alive.

00:36:06.080 --> 00:36:07.420 line:80%
As long as he is here,

00:36:08.200 --> 00:36:10.130 line:80%
the Northwest will remain stable.

00:36:17.430 --> 00:36:19.470 line:80%
Dry weather!

00:36:19.420 --> 00:36:23.420 line:80%
[Tofu]

00:36:20.310 --> 00:36:23.280 line:80%
Beware of fire!

00:36:31.600 --> 00:36:33.260 line:80%
Lin'an is indeed a nice place.

00:36:34.810 --> 00:36:36.500 line:80%
If I can settle down one day,

00:36:38.530 --> 00:36:39.720 line:80%
I'd also like to live such a

00:36:39.720 --> 00:36:41.780 line:80%
carefree life like a drifting cloud.

00:37:06.160 --> 00:37:08.310 line:80%
Did Lord Li really return to the Capital?

00:37:08.310 --> 00:37:10.120 line:80%
I met him on my way home.

00:37:10.760 --> 00:37:13.070 line:80%
He said now that the matter with Guo
has been resolved,

00:37:13.070 --> 00:37:14.640 line:80%
he must go back to Lucheng
to report first,

00:37:14.640 --> 00:37:15.900 line:80%
then go to the Capital.

00:37:26.460 --> 00:37:27.590 line:80%
What else did he say?

00:37:28.280 --> 00:37:30.610 line:80%
He asked when my parents arrived in Lin'an

00:37:30.760 --> 00:37:33.070 line:80%
and if I remember what happened
16 years ago.

00:37:33.070 --> 00:37:34.560 line:80%
I was only 2 then.

00:37:34.640 --> 00:37:36.100 line:80%
How could I remember that?

00:37:36.430 --> 00:37:38.630 line:80%
I need to ask my grandfather about that.

00:37:40.640 --> 00:37:43.130 line:80%
Changning, we have roasted chestnuts.

00:37:43.720 --> 00:37:46.280 line:80%
Changyu, Zheng, look who's back.

00:37:46.350 --> 00:37:51.800 line:80%
[Be a Good Person]

00:37:49.320 --> 00:37:51.360 line:80%
Zheng didn't lie to me.

00:37:51.390 --> 00:37:53.140 line:80%
The falcon is really back.

00:37:56.120 --> 00:37:57.850 line:80%
You're so good at taming birds?

00:37:58.310 --> 00:38:01.310 line:80%
Maybe you just fed it too well,

00:38:01.390 --> 00:38:02.990 line:80%
so it couldn't bear to leave.

00:38:03.350 --> 00:38:04.640 line:80%
Is it that greedy?

00:38:06.430 --> 00:38:08.030 line:80%
Since you know how to come home,

00:38:08.030 --> 00:38:10.420 line:80%
I won't lock you in the cage anymore.

00:38:10.790 --> 00:38:11.800 line:80%
You can be free.

00:38:25.120 --> 00:38:26.600 line:80%
It's just like me.

00:38:26.680 --> 00:38:28.950 line:80%
Was it born of my mother too?

00:38:28.970 --> 00:38:29.820 line:80%
Yes.

00:38:30.310 --> 00:38:32.240 line:80%
Raising it also needs a lot of food.

00:38:35.350 --> 00:38:35.950 line:80%
Here.

00:38:46.680 --> 00:38:49.280 line:80%
The dream in the Fengyu Pavilion
has ended.

00:38:51.760 --> 00:38:52.950 line:80%
Baffling.

00:38:58.200 --> 00:38:59.060 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:38:59.280 --> 00:39:01.880 line:80%
that rascal Li Huai'an
has really left Lin'an.

00:39:01.910 --> 00:39:04.570 line:80%
Mr. Gongsun's diversion tactic
really worked.

00:39:06.240 --> 00:39:07.310 line:80%
I'm also curious about

00:39:07.310 --> 00:39:08.990 line:80%
what tricks that brat used.

00:39:09.030 --> 00:39:09.640 line:80%
By the way,

00:39:09.910 --> 00:39:11.950 line:80%
at the border
between Yanzhou and Chongzhou,

00:39:11.950 --> 00:39:13.600 line:80%
bandits have been raiding military grain.

00:39:13.600 --> 00:39:15.030 line:80%
Wei Xuan was furious this time

00:39:15.030 --> 00:39:17.630 line:80%
and ordered them
to be wiped out within 10 days.

00:39:19.040 --> 00:39:20.620 line:80%
What kind of bandits have a death wish

00:39:20.620 --> 00:39:22.800 line:80%
to repeatedly
rob government grain convoys?

00:39:22.800 --> 00:39:25.000 line:80%
It must be Prince Changxin behind this.

00:39:27.080 --> 00:39:28.430 line:80%
That fool Wei Xuan

00:39:29.100 --> 00:39:30.900 line:80%
is about to fall into their trap.

00:39:32.080 --> 00:39:34.080 line:80%
Keep monitoring all recent intelligence

00:39:34.080 --> 00:39:35.310 line:80%
about the grain.

00:39:35.870 --> 00:39:36.470 line:80%
Yes.

00:39:36.910 --> 00:39:37.510 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:39:37.510 --> 00:39:39.200 line:80%
it's late. You should head back and rest

00:39:39.200 --> 00:39:40.730 line:80%
before the Marchioness...

00:39:41.680 --> 00:39:43.120 line:80%
be-becomes suspicious.

00:39:51.650 --> 00:39:53.910 line:80%
My stupid mouth ran faster than my brain.

00:39:53.930 --> 00:39:55.390 line:80%
I blurted out my thoughts.

00:39:55.870 --> 00:39:56.680 line:80%
Let's go.

00:40:10.320 --> 00:40:14.700 line:80%
[Enjoy Yourself]

00:40:17.580 --> 00:40:18.310 line:80%
Manager.

00:40:18.680 --> 00:40:19.990 line:80%
Manager Zhao from the Lin'an Rice Shop

00:40:19.990 --> 00:40:21.240 line:80%
booked a private room on the second floor

00:40:21.240 --> 00:40:22.080 line:80%
to entertain an important guest.

00:40:22.080 --> 00:40:22.760 line:80%
Look,

00:40:23.430 --> 00:40:25.950 line:80%
he ordered our best wine and dishes.

00:40:27.640 --> 00:40:29.030 line:80%
Okay, I got it.

00:40:29.030 --> 00:40:29.910 line:80%
Go get things ready.

00:40:29.910 --> 00:40:30.910 line:80%
I'll go up to greet them in a moment.

00:40:30.910 --> 00:40:31.470 line:80%
Alright.

00:40:37.990 --> 00:40:39.490 line:80%
[Heaven-class]

00:40:40.990 --> 00:40:42.310 line:80%
Manager Zhao.

00:40:43.120 --> 00:40:45.680 line:80%
Taking time out of your busy schedule
to visit Yixiang Restaurant,

00:40:45.680 --> 00:40:47.640 line:80%
it's truly an honor for us.

00:40:48.290 --> 00:40:52.010 line:80%
[Zhao Xun, Manager of Lin'an Rice Shop]

00:40:49.120 --> 00:40:50.790 line:80%
Manager Yu, you're too polite.

00:40:50.790 --> 00:40:52.190 line:80%
How is business today?

00:40:53.510 --> 00:40:55.580 line:80%
Business is good, of course.

00:41:05.310 --> 00:41:07.510 line:80%
May I ask who this guest is?

00:41:08.350 --> 00:41:10.390 line:80%
This is a rice merchant from the Capital,

00:41:10.390 --> 00:41:11.310 line:80%
Mr. Qi.

00:41:11.650 --> 00:41:14.580 line:80%
[Qi Min]

00:41:11.800 --> 00:41:14.200 line:80%
He's here
to discuss some business with me.

00:41:15.240 --> 00:41:17.640 line:80%
So you are a distinguished guest
from afar.

00:41:18.030 --> 00:41:20.290 line:80%
I hope the food and wine suit your tastes.

00:41:20.430 --> 00:41:21.510 line:80%
If you need anything,

00:41:21.510 --> 00:41:22.840 line:80%
please just let me know.

00:41:24.430 --> 00:41:26.230 line:80%
The food and wine are excellent.

00:41:27.390 --> 00:41:29.940 line:80%
Especially this Snow Bun Soup.

00:41:31.640 --> 00:41:33.690 line:80%
This is our signature dish.

00:41:35.080 --> 00:41:36.310 line:80%
To serve such an distinguished guest

00:41:36.310 --> 00:41:37.650 line:80%
is my honor.

00:41:38.120 --> 00:41:40.030 line:80%
Let me propose a toast to you.

00:42:12.680 --> 00:42:14.760 line:80%
Let me know if you need anything else.

00:42:14.950 --> 00:42:16.350 line:80%
Manager Yu, please wait.

00:42:16.870 --> 00:42:18.430 line:80%
Mr. Qi, you might not know,

00:42:18.990 --> 00:42:21.850 line:80%
but I haven't been
running a shop in Lin'an for long.

00:42:22.170 --> 00:42:24.630 line:80%
But Manager Yu has been in business
for years

00:42:24.760 --> 00:42:26.620 line:80%
and knows the local network best.

00:42:26.830 --> 00:42:28.980 line:80%
If you have any business ideas,

00:42:29.560 --> 00:42:32.510 line:80%
you could ask Manager Yu for advice.

00:42:37.080 --> 00:42:39.800 line:80%
What business are you planning, sir?

00:42:39.950 --> 00:42:42.010 line:80%
I am not familiar with the rice trade.

00:42:42.560 --> 00:42:44.950 line:80%
But if you want
to collaborate with someone,

00:42:44.950 --> 00:42:47.010 line:80%
I can introduce you to a few managers.

00:42:49.080 --> 00:42:51.140 line:80%
Manager Yu, you are very experienced

00:42:51.150 --> 00:42:52.350 line:80%
in receiving guests.

00:42:53.720 --> 00:42:56.050 line:80%
It seems you really do know
a lot of people.

00:43:03.600 --> 00:43:05.240 line:80%
Our shop serves guests from all over.

00:43:05.240 --> 00:43:07.010 line:80%
We believe harmony brings wealth.

00:43:07.010 --> 00:43:08.090 line:80%
In business,

00:43:08.310 --> 00:43:10.720 line:80%
it's always good to know more people.

00:43:11.910 --> 00:43:13.140 line:80%
It's all for business.

00:43:13.140 --> 00:43:14.310 line:80%
I understand.

00:43:27.200 --> 00:43:28.870 line:80%
Please enjoy yourselves.

00:43:28.870 --> 00:43:30.810 line:80%
I will go attend to other guests.

00:43:30.830 --> 00:43:31.950 line:80%
Please go ahead, Manager Yu.